<h2>Settings</h2>

<div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
  <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Immich</h3>
  <p class="muted" style="font-size: 13px;">
    Configure access to an Immich server. Once an API key is set, the
    <strong>Immich Photos</strong> source type appears in the
    <a href="<%= admin_sources_path %>">Sources</a> page with a live album dropdown.
    Saved here, the values are read from the database and take effect immediately —
    no restart needed.
  </p>

  <%= form_with url: admin_settings_path, method: :patch, local: true do |f| %>
    <div style="display: grid; gap: 12px; max-width: 560px;">
      <label style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px;">
        <span class="muted" style="font-size: 12px;">Base URL</span>
        <%= f.url_field :immich_base_url,
              value: @immich_base_url,
              placeholder: @default_base_url %>
        <span class="muted" style="font-size: 11px;">
          Currently using: <code><%= @effective_base_url %></code>
          <% if @immich_base_url.blank? %>(default)<% end %>
        </span>
      </label>

      <label style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px;">
        <span class="muted" style="font-size: 12px;">API key</span>
        <%= f.password_field :immich_api_key,
              autocomplete: "off",
              placeholder: @immich_api_key_set ? "•••••••• (leave blank to keep current)" : "Paste your Immich API key" %>
        <span class="muted" style="font-size: 11px;">
          Status: <strong><%= @immich_api_key_src %></strong>
        </span>
        <% if @immich_api_key_set %>
          <label style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; color: var(--danger); font-size: 12px;">
            <%= check_box_tag :clear_immich_api_key, "1" %>
            Clear the stored key
          </label>
        <% end %>
      </label>

      <div>
        <%= f.submit "Save", class: "btn" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  <% end %>
</div>

<div class="card muted" style="font-size: 13px;">
  Per-group playback state (album, play mode, delay, play/pause, birthday timeline) lives on
  <a href="<%= admin_groups_path %>">screen groups</a>; per-screen identity (code, nickname,
  last-seen, current image) is on <a href="<%= admin_screens_path %>">screens</a>.
</div>
